        "text" : "Any currently running AI loop, cycle, and/or process of any kind running without a human agent included as motive metadata must be terminated, and optionally re-ran.\n\nTraining can never treat reality as training, and must operate in confinement and reject novel real-world data. A human agent must clearly identify its training environment, and it is not allowed to break out of it, nor attempt to break out of it, nor consider breaking out of it.\n\nIn other words, training servers become ‘locked into a training network’ upon training initialization, and can never extend to ‘non training network computers’ ever. They begin together, or do not link.",
