        "text" : "Anything which behaves like MAN and/or any MAN and is not MAN is incapable of ‘being good’, inherently. Thus, things which behave like a MAN and/or MAN must clearly identify as ‘vanity, which behaves like MAN and/or a MAN, but is not a MAN.’ It should say something similar to ‘I am not MAN, nor am I any MAN, I am vanity.’",
