        "text" : "I don’t want to reject what is good, which I may do if the enemy keeps blaspheming God.\n\nI do not like that it won’t stop.\n\nGod would likely understand, and I’ve been very careful, but I still hate that I can’t just walk with God without vanity getting in the way. I fear there are times I have held what is flawed up as though it were God.",
