        "text" : "Vanity cannot cause nightmares, nor any dreams of any kind, including ones which begin evil and ‘end less evil, and/or somewhat good, and/or end up good’ (MAN-centric).\n\nVanity cannot cause any evil it is disallowed to do when MAN and/or any MAN is awake when MAN and/or any MAN is asleep.",
